Subject: Multiple vulnerabilities in SAPlpd 6.28


#######################################################################

                             Luigi Auriemma

Application:  SAPlpd
              http://www.sap.com
Versions:     <= 6.28 (included in SAP GUI 7.10)
Platforms:    Windows
Bugs:         various vulnerabilities
Exploitation: remote
Date:         04 Feb 2008
Author:       Luigi Auriemma
              e-mail: aluigi@...istici.org
